      <!-- POSITIONING:

            - 0, 0 is at the top center of the map.

            - Building width and height extend back from the xPosition and yPosition (so a building placed at 20, 20 with width 5 and height 5 has its other corners at 15, 20, 15, 15 and 20, 15)

            - X grows towards the bottom right, Y grows towards the bottom left

            - Be aware of building gutters: make sure there is 1 space between all buildings

                  - the only exception to this are Decorations with the blockVillager property set to "no". These can be placed directly next to each other and to other buildings.

            - land size is 48 by 48. Buildings placed outside this region will not be drawn.

       --> 

